scenes.description: Gura talks about her birthday and upcoming merchandise releases while sitting at a celebratory table.
Gura expresses her nervousness and prepares to transition to singing to calm down.
Gura asks the audience to close their eyes during a visual transition to her 3D stage performance environment.
Gura showcases her 3D underwater stage, thanks her fans, and celebrates reaching 4 million subscribers.
